parameters:
Information Broker Leon: According to the old map, there's
no doubt that this is the place.

Information Broker Leon: However, it seems that we need to
solve the mystery of this stone tablet.

Mage Relm: This... looks similar to the Devil Bedon's magic
circle, doesn't it?
Information Broker Leon: Can you read this, kid!?

Mage Relm: How rude... I am the genius of the Magic
Academy, you know!

Information Broker Leon: I'm on a roll here! I think this
code on the old map is a hint to solve the mystery of the
stone tablet!

Mage Relm: Alright, I understand. This great genius will
easily decipher it for you!
Mage Relm: If it's up to me, something like this is easy--

Mage Relm: Honestly, can't you at least say thank you
once!

Mage Relm: It seems to be the place that was sealed. The
request to be their escort might have been the right choice
after all.
Clea: Let's go inside too. We can't let the client die.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
